Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.26,0:01:25.48,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}想试着谈场猜谜般的恋爱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.02,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星星在呢喃着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:30.94,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}虽然害怕…但还是想！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:36.40,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}光是安稳度日 也太无趣了点
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:41.16,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}真希望能改变些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:44.87,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}既然想要个契机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:46.54,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}那就飞奔出去吧 Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:50.71,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}回忆在骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:56.30,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我…好像认识你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不论是晴天雨天还是在下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:03.18,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我都好想好想去见你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:04.60,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}从过去到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:05.85,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}从明天到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.73,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}是啊 时间 Nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:14.53,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}先前烦恼的事情 通通都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:20.41,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}来展开新的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:25.50,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}又在做梦吗？现在的梦还不能说！
