Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.00,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}下雨天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:36.09,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不管是怎样的天气 I need you!!
